{"tid":168344,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇批發賣日本飲品 食品網推介？","createTime":"2017-03-23T13:14:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T20:22:05.000Z","uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ce1c5c294b356dbd910bd416aa721066822622aa","tid":168344,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T13:14:29.000Z","msg":"因為759仲未有網店，所以就上網搵下有冇d類似既網店係賣日本零食<br />\n<br />\n搵左陣之後，估唔到原來一直都係有呢d批發網，可以一箱箱咁買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />買滿幾舊水仲可以送上門<br />\ne.g.<br />\n<a href=\"http://39043118.com/categories/支裝飲品(批發)/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F39043118.com%2Fcategories%2F%E6%94%AF%E8%A3%9D%E9%A3%B2%E5%93%81%28%E6%89%B9%E7%99%BC%29%2F&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=4c4baaab\" target=\"_blank\">http://39043118.com/categories/支裝飲品(批發)/</a><br />\n<br />\n不過搵黎搵去都搵唔到d又平又多野揀既鋪頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係有野飲冇零食 ，一係冇野飲有零食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然聽過有一間觀塘工廠區既鋪頭d野都好平，但係太遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又冇網店<br />\n<br />\n酒水已備<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求巴絲們推介好店<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400c9b9d0ad4e41ef042cebc45c6dc6114a605dc","tid":168344,"uid":59528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T13:33:41.000Z","msg":"我之前睇過aeon個批發網<br />\n幾多日式飲品同零食<br />\n不過一個人食唔曬一箱<br />\n不了"},{"pid":"2904c29a5e2642cc03628baab2c97179694f1cce","tid":168344,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T13:45:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我之前睇過aeon個批發網<br />\n幾多日式飲品同零食<br />\n不過一個人食唔曬一箱<br />\n不了</blockquote><br />\n佢個價同出面差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有d仲貴過我屋企附近d鋪仔"},{"pid":"da49713ba6729d58bd628ecc3ad285beb064b277","tid":168344,"uid":36849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"